00:34:04,118 --> 00:34:05,819
Now, I don't want to get too abstract

559
00:34:05,939 --> 00:34:07,520
on the theory of negative space and how

560
00:34:07,560 --> 00:34:10,421
that translates to simplicity in larger game systems.

