00:36:22,415 --> 00:36:22,656
But...

592
00:36:23,713 --> 00:36:28,015
it inherited that same complex navigation network from the Egyptian version.

593
00:36:28,555 --> 00:36:33,877
This means Face Classic also inherited the same imbalances and poor flow

594
00:36:34,298 --> 00:36:35,538
as seen in the Egyptian version.

