00:36:36,198 --> 00:36:39,159
Unreal Tournament 2004 was an update to the engine

596
00:36:39,279 --> 00:36:40,820
rather than a whole new engine,

597
00:36:41,340 --> 00:36:46,002
so the Egyptian and Classic versions were built in the context of the same game systems.

