00:40:02,071 --> 00:40:06,716
and problem-solving, to improve gameplay in your maps, you need to minimize memory load

653
00:40:06,836 --> 00:40:09,058
so your players can comprehend their environment.

654
00:40:09,619 --> 00:40:12,381
You need to reduce attention-switching to keep them focused.

